				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">THAT is what the current situation is like. Dont try and fool yourselfs into thinking that some poor step father was in such dire need and Oaga the saviour came along and did what was necessary. Oaga didnt even give the community of "friends" a chance, first option was a sell out, he didnt let them know of what mioght happen, he didnt give them a chance to help donate or fomulate ideas together on how his problem could be solved. There are lots of intelligent people in the beastlord community and Oaga did not bother tapping into any of them for help with his problem. Instead he sold everyones work and benefited soley from it... where is the money for the other mods hard work? what share did they get from making this site great how it use to be? I bet oaga wont bother to show his appreciation and give them a cent</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Get a grip, huh? Ever here the word 'volunteer' ? Go do it. Donate 100s of hours at a hospital or something. Make that thousands of hours. If someone with a lot of cash comes along and buys that hospital, that sale has nothing what-so-ever in any way or stretch of the imagination has anything to do with your volunteer work. 
<br />

<br />
Every mod that has ever been here has been a willing volunteer. Suddenly, in your view, they are now partners or CEOs or something. No, they are volunteers, and thats all.
<br />

<br />
Lets all get a serious grip on where we direct our anger as well. Oago, from the creation of this site, has been nothing but helpful to this community. This cummunity wouldn't even be here if not for him. He's been serving us all for years, and freely at that.
<br />

<br />
No, I don't believe suddenly the alien pod people have infected his mind and made him now into the Evil Oago. He's the same Oago he has always been, who recently had to make some serious choices in a very short amount of time. This was a RL crisis. Who among you, while having a RL crisis even thinks of solving it in the virtual world of online message boards?
<br />

<br />
Oago has explained a zillion times what happened, and you know, we're still here posting here talking about it- there aren't any Evil alien pod people after me! Very little has changed actually, with the exception of a single ad at the top of the page which you are freely allowed to ignore or click on. 
<br />

<br />
If the plat and toon selling bothers you that much, then the best place to direct that anger is to the entity that has let it grow, and that entity is Sony. They created the problem, and unlike Verant, who actually spent a great deal of time trying hard to squash the cheats, loopholes and bugs that allows this behavior to go on, Sony has all but ignored it. 
<br />

<br />
People like Yantis are only taking advantage of these loopholes, but if Sony would fix the loopholes, much the same way Blizzard did on the first Diablo release, there would be no Yantis and no problem.
<br />

<br />
But Sony really doesn't care that much about the balance of the economy or the various plat farm cheats. They are not Blizzard. As long as you keep logging on and playing, and your not bitching about them to them, they see no reason to change a thing.
<br />

<br />
Directing anger at Oago or this community accomplishes nothing. It shouldn't be about you and your anger, it should be about the problem with the game and how the hell are we ever going to get it fixed.
<br />

<br />
Until everyone stops being 'destructive' and starts being 'constructive' nothing has a chance to improve. So everyone, take a deep breath, and really think about it.
<br />

<br />
edit: And speaking of volunteer work, I would be completely happy to volunteer some of my time to any of the ladies in helping out on those breast examinations. Sometimes a second opinion can be helpful- just drop me a PM. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
